data.description: Welcome to your dream WATERFRONT property in Pensacola, Florida! This 4-bed, 2.5-bath gem is complete with a gorgeous balcony POOL, stunning panoramic views, and a convenient ELEVATOR connecting all floors! As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting and open floor plan which includes...The spacious living room which features large windows that flood the space with natural light, highlighting the beautiful luxury vinyl floors that flow throughout the home, along with a gourmet kitchen on the main level, which boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space and a convenient island. On the main level, you'll also discover the spacious primary suite, with views of your own private balcony pool with waterfront views. The master suite is complete with a walk-in closet & an en-suite bathroom with double vanity, a soaking tub & a separate shower! Two additional bedrooms on this level offer plenty of space for family or guests, and they share a well-appointed full bathroom. Upstairs, on the top level of the home features your 4th Bedroom or office space with storage area. One of the true highlights of this property is the expansive back deck, where you'll find a pristine pool, perfect for cooling off on hot Florida days along with a FENCED in BACK YARD. The best part... NO HOA, this home is conveniently located near top-rated schools, shopping, dining, and the beautiful Perdido Key Beach! Some favorite locations are the Blue Angel Recreational Park with boat launch, Escambia County Recreational Park, and the Tarlin Bayou National Park, all within 5 minutes away. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to make this your forever home, or your new favorite investment property!
